<p>What is on this site:</p>
<ul>
<li>Below you will find all the breaking music news updated almost every hour.</li>
<li>On the left hand side you can find a link for join our mailing list where we give out free rap beat making information.</li>
<li>At the top you will find a contact us link if you have any questions.</li>
</ul>
<p>I hope you enjoy the site, speak soon&#8230;</p>
